      • build

        RULE_KEY build(BuildRule buildRule)
        Creates a new RULE_KEY for the given BuildRule. In most cases RULE_KEY is going to be RuleKey, but it can be anything really.
        Parameters:
        buildRule - The build rule to create the key for.
        Returns:
        A rule key.

      • getFromCache

        @Nullable
default RULE_KEY getFromCache(BuildRule buildRule)
        Returns a RULE_KEY from an internal cache, if possible. If a non-null value is returned, it is guaranteed to be he same as if build(com.facebook.buck.core.rules.BuildRule) were called instead.
